From: T510-AI Builder <builder@example.com>
Date: 2026-03-30
Subject: Enable NI XGE Management Ethernet driver for T510-AI

Enable CONFIG_NI_XGE_MANAGEMENT_ENET=y in xilinx_zynqmp_defconfig
for National Instruments XGE management ethernet support.

Signed-off-by: T510-AI Builder <builder@example.com>
---
 arch/arm64/configs/xilinx_zynqmp_defconfig | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/configs/xilinx_zynqmp_defconfig b/arch/arm64/configs/xilinx_zynqmp_defconfig
index xxxxxxx..xxxxxxx 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/configs/xilinx_zynqmp_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm64/configs/xilinx_zynqmp_defconfig
@@ -71,6 +71,7 @@ CONFIG_XILINX_AXI_EMAC=y
 CONFIG_AMD_PHY=y
 CONFIG_BROADCOM_PHY=y
 CONFIG_BCM7XXX_PHY=y
+CONFIG_NI_XGE_MANAGEMENT_ENET=y
 CONFIG_BCM87XX_PHY=y
 CONFIG_CICADA_PHY=y
 CONFIG_DAVICOM_PHY=y
-- 
2.xx.x